It’s depleting morale, ruining the reputation of our military, and needs to stop.

“White Privilege: Unpacking the Invisible Knapsack”

The manual argues that everything should be viewed through the lens of privilege and racism, and seeks to debunk any notion of a “meritocracy.” It’s exactly the sort of woke ideology that should be nowhere near our military.
